r />\n但佢唔會話我知<br />\n我講佢又話唔好成日講 會好煩"},{"pid":"0ef197054b41aa2231bf58424dd44022b8a211d9","tid":322431,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:02:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6cd1e19e45bd1cc4763c267195d0ffbea2939dc","tid":322431,"uid":13032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:07:25.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n硬係覺得佢對我啲野冇乜興趣咁"},{"pid":"8177b36d09672755095b0d358f07a6ca31ddc299","tid":322431,"uid":44549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:54:45.000Z","msg":"哞屌 我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條女真心on9 <br />\n一係就覆啲懶有道理嘅野<br />\n明明自己唔開心都唔會想聽呢啲野<br />\n成日想屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352ba2d75af37e1fd6eb05025240cd807dad3e11","tid":322431,"uid":87319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:05:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n硬係覺得佢對我啲野冇乜興趣咁</blockquote><br />\n巴打個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我條女好多方面都好好 又唔港女又無咩脾氣 又唔會好癡身<br />\n唯獨是呢樣野難搞啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底係我要求太高定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但要佢就我改變自己又好似好煩 好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5d87ee1eca107f38055fe93e4405de248a3eb3","tid":322431,"uid":87319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲friend一係就兩邊都係咁，屎尿屁都可以講好耐，咩topic都講得，一係就好似你女朋友咁一兩秒錄音或者藍tick，但佢地本身又覺得冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得咁樣相處係ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 自己同女朋友係乜都傾果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地平時都係乜都傾得 但一到我自己既野佢就真係無咩興趣知咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3aceeddb2d79a00c3d2d5ac7814e0eb6106dde","tid":322431,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:11:08.000Z","msg":"Ex都係咁<br />\n我返工既佢就只會話返工係咁嫁啦<br />\n佢返學既我要照單全收仲要記低佢講乜"},{"pid":"537f167a1ab4bc54ddc3f8411efbdd83c511a3c8","tid":322431,"uid":73152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:12:58.000Z","msg":"其實係咪個個女仔都係咁？依家個個係咁ex又係咁<br />\n有時比左慰藉你 都想唔開心時有點慰藉<br />\n但換來多數係hea覆幾粒字 到你用返差唔多態度回應 就會比對方話到七彩 又話唔關心她"},{"pid":"993a9468936e82bdb899db1defabc1e965601975","tid":322431,"uid":22632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:15:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有啲friend一係就兩邊都係咁，屎尿屁都可以講好耐，咩topic都講得，一係就好似你女朋友咁一兩秒錄音或者藍tick，但佢地本身又覺得冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得咁樣相處係ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 自己同女朋友係乜都傾果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地平時都係乜都傾得 但一到我自己既野佢就真係無咩興趣知咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>戇鳩仔<br />\n佢好明顯自鳩私啦<br />\n同埋你愛佢多過佢愛你"},{"pid":"2faf6a44980b6336a7ac154b436d2bff325786f9","tid":322431,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:15:52.000Z","msg":"有唔少心事都係源自於條女，點分享比佢聽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f50230e8c1a6527c0ff969649f5ff2f50270f00","tid":322431,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa7d47877440b0fa7e715ab8954fa8803f0423f","tid":322431,"uid":13032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:00:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪個個女仔都係咁？依家個個係咁ex又係咁<br />\n有時比左慰藉你 都想唔開心時有點慰藉<br />\n但換來多數係hea覆幾粒字 到你用返差唔多態度回應 就會比對方話到七彩 又話唔關心她</blockquote><br />\n完全一9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9c2d916b4d7fb458dae44305eba61703794071","tid":322431,"uid":2342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:07:31.000Z","msg":"我都唔會講心事比男友聽<br />\n一黎佢根本唔明我既感受，我地價值觀唔同<br />\n二黎佢講唔到我想聽既野<br />\n三黎廢事煩，講左心事佢都幫我唔到嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n我唔開心個陣，我真係唔想聽咩「唔好唔開心」、「唔好比咁大壓力自己」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}